{"tid":49372,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是咁的，我今日整左個「紫薯抹茶流心芝士海膽批」","createTime":"2016-12-21T16:04:54.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-22T01:42:25.000Z","uid":68594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4e368da855fb2459653feaedb87bac051d1f712c","tid":49372,"uid":68594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T16:04:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一切諗頭都係源於<br />\n猛鳩語錄<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/man9secret/photos/a.308083632886195.1073741827.308079482886610/369863783374846/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fman9secret%2Fphotos%2Fa.308083632886195.1073741827.308079482886610%2F369863783374846%2F&d=aAykAqn9Fjiz0GAmjPOR9HvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=a68dbc7d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/man9secret/photos/a.308083632886195.1073741827.308079482886610/369863783374846/</a>個post，<br />\n身為抹茶，芝士，同海膽愛好者&amp;#22021;我，簡直覺得依個完美&amp;#22021;結合！<br />\n為&amp;#21655;依一個商機仲未畀&amp;#21874;餐廳發掘出&amp;#22175;，<br />\n今日我就要先拔頭籤整左佢出&amp;#22175;，再落個註冊商標，<br />\n香港第二個李嘉誠仲唔係我！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n為左令我大家都有機會試到，所以我所有&amp;#22021;原材料都係買返&amp;#22175;&amp;#22021;！分別有係一田買返&amp;#22175;&amp;#22021;特價海膽，20X$<br />\n<img src=\"https://s23.postimg.org/p1p5lwjp7/PC216138.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs23.postimg.org%2Fp1p5lwjp7%2FPC216138.jpg&h=a006e9b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n半熟工房&amp;#22021;流心芝士批，22$<br />\n<img src=\"https://s23.postimg.org/ipa0c2gmz/PC216139.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs23.postimg.org%2Fipa0c2gmz%2FPC216139.jpg&h=3cf6f337&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n聖安娜&amp;#22021;紫薯批，19$<br />\n<img src=\"https://s23.postimg.org/vupii6aij/PC216140.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs23.postimg.org%2Fvupii6aij%2FPC216140.jpg&h=4c9ad738&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n東海堂&amp;#22021;抹茶唔知咩甜品杯，20$<br />\n<img src=\"https://s23.postimg.org/n0ym12njv/PC216141.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs23.postimg.org%2Fn0ym12njv%2FPC216141.jpg&h=02f25ff2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n為左令到佢更加有流心&amp;#22021;效果，當然要放佢入微波爐叮30秒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://s23.postimg.org/5cbgn716j/PC216142.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs23.postimg.org%2F5cbgn716j%2FPC216142.jpg&h=58e41b8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後就將個紫薯批上面&amp;#22000;&amp;#21874;紫薯蓉刮佢出&amp;#22175;，再用精美&amp;#22021;技巧放&amp;#21946;一個暖暖地&amp;#22021;芝士撻上面，暫時都仲係正正常常<br />\n<img src=\"https://s23.postimg.org/b1rp7i7cr/PC216143.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs23.postimg.org%2Fb1rp7i7cr%2FPC216143.jpg&h=2156e52e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後再將東海堂&amp;#22021;抹茶唔知咩甜品杯上面&amp;#22021;抹茶寒天果凍同抹茶忌廉放係側邊，由於芝士撻有少少暖，&amp;#21874;紫薯用開始溶化，睇&amp;#22175;要加快速度！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://s23.postimg.org/3ztrlb3qz/PC216145.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs23.postimg.org%2F3ztrlb3qz%2FPC216145.jpg&h=39492efe&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"80ec7e6e4ad5448cb50dda80911e2067f7d6d90e","tid":49372,"uid":21181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T16:05:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4ccd8679e73bf11849499869ff77f77bd30341af","tid":49372,"uid":68594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T16:06:20.000Z","msg":"屌，啲字錯哂"},{"pid":"8df1d220e0a0f16920f3f6ca02894ba8d5f675dc","tid":49372,"uid":34676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T16:08:47.000Z","msg":"猛鳩話你好有創意WO"},{"pid":"d5cc658ea384aa1fab6f25da519f2eee327f93d9","tid":49372,"uid":11030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T16:23:49.000Z","msg":"見到紫薯放左落去個下已經笑出聲"},{"pid":"9db8817b1ada2ad96f4b9b83a1ebd7c9f00e1daa","tid":49372,"uid":9942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T01:42:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>猛鳩話你好有創意WO</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}